resources.string: Welcome to your first jam search!

Next you will need to enter an area where you will want to look for people who want to jam with you. Yes, with you!
You can do this by manually entering a location or allowing us to find them in your current environment.
In the future, you can always change the search area manually.

Do you want us to search for your current location?
Hi, lets find people to jam with
